[30;1m11 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m12 | [0m[35mdef _build_uuidv7(timestamp: int, node: int) -> UUID:[0m
[30;1m13 | [0m[35m    # merge timestamp and node into 128-bit UUID[0m
[30;1m14 | [0m[35m    # timestamp is first 48 bits, node is last 80 bits[0m
[30;1m15 | [0m[35m    uuid_int = (timestamp & 0xFFFFFFFFFFFF) << 80[0m
[30;1m16 | [0m[35m    uuid_int |= node & 0xFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFF[0m
